  "2210500": {
    "name": "VetVR Veterinary Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 2210500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/bc052e0e1170d9b72f067117e8217d4d.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=275 /></span><br>这是VetVR 兽医模拟器的<strong>抢先体验版</strong>，由真正的兽医领导的小型但充满激情的独立工作室开发。我们正在与科罗拉多州立大学兽医教学医院合作开发这款游戏，很高兴将您的反馈纳入最终游戏。请在我们的社区中心告诉我们您的想法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/17117efaa941a25d584f14abaaa56c6e.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>您刚从兽医学校毕业就被录用了。您的新雇主认识到您的才能和对动物的热爱，他们选择了您来帮助他们开设全新的兽医诊所！通过为各类客户提供高水准的护理，向他们展示您在学校所学到的一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/af1dc1058514f1a9d83e8ccb8d32568a.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/4e418d0b71bd90b3666288801482c705.poster.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/4e418d0b71bd90b3666288801482c705.webm?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/4e418d0b71bd90b3666288801482c705.mp4?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>诊断和治疗复杂的医疗状况、神秘的创伤和其他紧急情况！依据动物的行为、病历和其他报告（例如 X 光和血液测试）为您的病人确诊。找到正确的治疗方法，并记住每个决定都会对您的患者产生积极或消极的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/7eb9dd6523e10c92069b3c2037e5235f.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/6f8b68fd785085a9883b47783b782b30.poster.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/6f8b68fd785085a9883b47783b782b30.webm?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/6f8b68fd785085a9883b47783b782b30.mp4?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>徜徉在由拥有硕士和博士的兽医们创建的多级别培训游戏中，温习所有兽医基础知识。无论以前的知识水平如何，增强您作为兽医的信心，并练习在瞬间做出影响动物患者生死的决定的能力。练习工具使用、测试、图表阅读和药物来治疗和治愈有不同需求的动物。每个病人都需要真正的兽医逻辑和技能。如果您做了错误的决定，您可以随时重启场景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/8721de0894a3136f10e2ab23b5ad440f.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/feb665af4418d4597a91542ac6d7ab7d.poster.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/feb665af4418d4597a91542ac6d7ab7d.webm?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/feb665af4418d4597a91542ac6d7ab7d.mp4?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当您完成各类场景时，不要忘记环顾四周。作为奖励，你可能会惊奇地发现有趣的复活节彩蛋，解锁隐藏的小游戏，和额外的新奇异的动物。在拯救生命的同时，花点时间在大厅放松一下，和诊所吉祥物布鲁斯一起玩接球游戏。他以偷任何含有碳水化合物的东西而闻名，所以当他在小吃店附近转悠时要小心看护。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/b794808ab903e3d6e87a164bfdc9fe8e.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/294964677f7d87613a00a300bcf13830.poster.avif?t=1724211217\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/294964677f7d87613a00a300bcf13830.webm?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210500/extras/294964677f7d87613a00a300bcf13830.mp4?t=1724211217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当您成功地治疗动物身上的小伤口到各类不明疾病，您会发现您的工作对周边人群产生了影响。您的顾客们谈论着您的诊所，甚至将其推荐给其他人。他们特别喜欢您照顾他们的宠物，而且您工作越努力，诊所的声誉就越高。解锁新的和令人兴奋的场景获得更多的奖励吧！有人说当地动物园正在该地区寻找更多兽医合作吗？我想我们很快会知道的！",
